text: Troarn is a commune. It is found in the Normandy region in the Calvados department in the northwest of France. On 1 January 2017, it was merged into the new commune of Saline,Arrêté préfectoral 29 July 2016 but this merger was undone on 31 December 2019. == References == Category:Communes in Calvados
title: Troarn
